Package de.tud.kom.p2psim.impl.scenario

Provides classes required to initialize the simulator run (i.e. scenario).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Parser Implementations of this interface are used by configurator to parse parameter values for scenario actions.
 

Class Summary
AbstractScenarioFactory Abstract factory which provides common functionality for XML-based and CSV-based action factories.
ConfigurationFileTest This test case is used to test ALL configuration files for consistency.
CSVScenarioFactory Factory to create a default scenario from a CSV file.
DefaultConfigurator The default implementation of the configuration mechanism.
DefaultHostBuilder This builder will parse an XML subtree and create hosts as specified there.
DOMScenarioFactory Factory to create a default scenario from a DOM subtree.
ExtendedScenarioAction Specifies which action and when should take place in the simulator.
ExtendedScenarioTest  
 

Package de.tud.kom.p2psim.impl.scenario Description

Provides classes required to initialize the simulator run (i.e. scenario). Most users will never have to deal with the content of this package.
